{"tid":1715642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"水警接中国學生離開中大校園　深圳共青團提供7天免費住宿","createTime":"2019-11-13T06:47:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T07:19:47.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ea7ab3f5d01e1f53add628c1cf0f4d480b18ed38","tid":1715642,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:47:59.000Z","msg":"警方表示，今早（13日）一批中大內地生基於安全理由打算搬離校園，但因為附近道路被暴徒放置雜物而嚴重阻塞，導致他們無法離開，於是聯絡警方尋求協助。警方基於安全考慮及附近路面出現堵路情況，決定調派水警輪協助該批學生前往安全地點。當抵達地點後，他們自行安排交通工具離開。<br />\n<br />\n另外，外交部駐港公署特派員表示，近日香港多所大學遭蒙面暴徒圍攻，很多內地在港學生前往深圳暫避；深圳共青團今日在社交媒體發帖稱，深圳青年驛站為內地在港學生提供7天免費住宿等服務。目前，全市8個區12家驛站，隨時歡迎內地在港學生入住。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20191113/s00001/e25fd71bff83108b3911481cf1020cb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20191113%2Fs00001%2Fe25fd71bff83108b3911481cf1020cb6.jpg&h=fbb32eb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191113/s00001/1573626294861/水警接中大內地生離開校園-深圳共青團提供7天免費住宿\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191113%2Fs00001%2F1573626294861%2F%E6%B0%B4%E8%AD%A6%E6%8E%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%9F%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%E6%A0%A1%E5%9C%92-%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%85%B1%E9%9D%92%E5%9C%98%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B7%E5%A4%A9%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%BF&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLadOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=5d05e8dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191113%2Fs00001%2F1573626294861%2F%E6%B0%B4%E8%AD%A6%E6%8E%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%9F%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%E6%A0%A1%E5%9C%92-%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%85%B1%E9%9D%92%E5%9C%98%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B7%E5%A4%A9%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%BF&h=862269d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191113/s00001/1573626294861/水警接中大內地生離開校園-深圳共青團提供7天免費住宿</a>"},{"pid":"763be80f5f71e627